WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:39.000 --> 00:00:41.810
 Cherrapunji is located in north-east India. 

00:00:41.850 --> 00:00:43.950
 I imagined an overcrowded place, 

00:00:43.990 --> 00:00:45.810
 full of people and noise ... 

00:00:45.850 --> 00:00:47.950
 Here, it's totally different. 

00:01:00.830 --> 00:01:02.880
 All this haze, this fog ... 

00:01:03.020 --> 00:01:04.840
 It's extraordinary. 

00:01:21.020 --> 00:01:25.000
 I think their sense of community is very strong. 

00:01:28.000 --> 00:01:30.900
 It's amazing, they are happy all the time. 

00:01:42.950 --> 00:01:46.870
 This place is beautiful. 

00:01:54.860 --> 00:01:58.900
 This people is particularly open, cheerful 

00:01:58.940 --> 00:01:59.950
 and placid. 

00:02:16.890 --> 00:02:18.790
 When the sky is clear, 

00:02:18.830 --> 00:02:22.010
 I understand why the people of Cherrapunji like to live here. 

00:02:22.910 --> 00:02:24.010
 This is really beautiful. 

